Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,--Who are you?\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Who the heck are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:01:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they also your subordinates, Captain Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?! Y-Yeah, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.06,0:02:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys lost your memories, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.35,0:02:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, pretty ladies! Your names, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, human! I'm a reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.03,0:02:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.05,0:02:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates this, pirates that! What a stupid era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate pirates! What I like\Nare money and tangerines!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that I'd\Nbe traveling with pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys're making quite a\Nracket so early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're interrupting my morning nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to get out of here somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got no idea what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but it seems like there's\Nno point in me staying here.
