Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Navigator...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can rest easy for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that unpleasant pirate\Nhunter is off the ship, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling that Navigator\Nmight set foot on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing her, she probably won't do too much
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,until she can make a level-headed decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm starving. I wanna eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You look tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez... You have no sense of tension, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But, well, I guess we can think about\Nwhat to do after we finish eating, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Miss, I didn't get your name yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,First, could you tell us about\Nthe memories that we lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No way that I'd stay in a place\Nlike that for even a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates cold-bloodedly steal\Nthings that people cherish!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to come up with a way to\Nreturn to Cocoyashi Village quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad... that you came, lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I welcome you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's awfully quiet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if something happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I'll find something\Nif I go up a bit higher...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Newspaper...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! This newspaper is\Nthe only thing I can depend on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna let you have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard! Stop screwing with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I give you something to go on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! It's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,--Who cares?!\N--Hey, who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If I knew, I wouldn't be having this problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.69,0:05:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hey...\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.31,0:05:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... So you're looking for a boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:06:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yeah.\N--The boats docked at this harbor\Nare the only boats on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They all seem to be in disrepair, as if\Nthey haven't been used in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that everyone is too busy\Nwith other things to care about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't believe me, go ahead\Nand go around the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a small island. It won't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, take it easy and stay a while.\NI'm sure you'll enjoy it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stay too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,--Oh, I see.\N--I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotten kinda sleepy. I'm going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys are real pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So clouds are really fluffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:07:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Daaachshund... Horsey-Bird...\NDarn it! Why can't I remember them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Davy Back Fight, the large Navy fortress...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sky islands and the sand country, Alabasta...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We really had such a grand journey?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.79,0:07:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The captain of this ship has a\N100-million-berry bounty on his head?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't you have some\Nmore neat adventure stories?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I joined your crew after you left Alabasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, unfortunately, I don't know\Nwhat happened before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn! That sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I have a hard time buying her story,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,it is true that the seasonings and equipment
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,are where I would like them to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin-san, could you tell us about the\Nmost crucial thing-- about yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Well then, let's include\Nthe ship's doctor, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, it's backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shut up, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hungry, aren't you?\NCome and eat with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Don't be ridiculous!\NI can't eat with humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask your opinion, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, our exceptional ship's doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Dummy! Praising me wouldn't\Nmake me feel happy! You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He sure looks happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We were traveling this area of sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami, are you really sure\Nwe're on the right track?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.56,0:08:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. The Log Pose\Nis pointing this direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp! Can't you see anything yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Err, hold on, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Ah! I see an island!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There are coral reefs scattered all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous to keep heading ashore like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's drop anchor off the coast\Ntonight and land tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying you don't\Nwanna listen to your navigator?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji-kun, Luffy won't be having dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,--What?!\N--Okay, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, everyone went to bed except\Nfor me, as I was doing some research,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and the swordsman, who was standing watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's not much, but that's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest is what you remember... probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Given the way the pirate hunter talked earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems he fell asleep\Npartway through the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It would seem so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like another cup?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, I wonder why only you\Ndidn't lose your memory, Robin-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If the swordsman was really asleep,\Nthe only difference between you guys and me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is that you were sleeping and I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I was asleep, I remember!\NI'm certain that we're the Usopp Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, sleep determined\Nwhether we lost our memory or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I just stated the facts, that's all.\NI can't draw any conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.09,0:09:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of such a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me the very last thing you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:10:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I went to pick\Nmedicinal herbs with Doktorin,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,returned to the castle and went to bed.\NAnd then, when I woke up, I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,As for me... Hey, you're ignoring me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I fainted after being\Nswallowed by a big whirlpool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And the next thing I knew, I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I went to bed in my room after work,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but when I woke up, I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't remember\Nanything after those points, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! I heard the sound\Nof a horn from somewhere and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.07,0:10:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A horn... Yeah, a horn! I heard it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.53,0:10:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A child suddenly appeared before my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me... It's not that\Nwe lost our memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...but in fact, that the kid\Nstole our memories from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's certain that he\Nholds the key to this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it possible that we'll lose more\Nmemories each time we fall asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,--Ahhhh!\N--Ahhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait. It happened in my dream, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A supernatural thing like that\Ncan't actually happen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how do you explain the fact\Nthat we all had the same dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Supernatural or not, it's the fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean to scare you,\Nbut in the worst-case scenario,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it's possible that you will no longer\Nbe able to tell who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! That scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why do you care if we\Nremember things or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, it sucks that I lost all those fun memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but we can just start over and go on\Nnew adventures together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't be ridiculous! We may\Nend up losing all our memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I-If that happens, our past\Nand dreams will all be--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream won't be lost. It must\Nbe the same for you guys, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What a positive thinker he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Our captain is the same...\Nwhether or not he has his memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He's kinda amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:12:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! My food is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch other people's food!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if he's crazy or what...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I feel like I'm an idiot for\Nthinking about things seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the town?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is kinda exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you making?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A new medicine for regaining\Nmemories! Don't interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,--Did you find something?\N--Ahhh! Don't touch that without asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,--No. It seems like an ordinary island.\N--Ugh! What the heck is this? It's bitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is, indeed, my great invention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for asking! Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...we don't have to worry\Neven if we lose our memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I name them, "My name board"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A question mark? That's rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a raccoon dog or emergency food!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stupid Lovelyn"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like my idea? Cool, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make stupid stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My memories... huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,People are such fragile things, Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lucky, Zoro. You're a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be the world's\Ngreatest swordsman, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:14:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, when girls grow up,\Nthey get weaker than men...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's frustrating!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If only... If only I had been born a man...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be whining like that after you beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not fair! You're my goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,--Zoro...\N--Boy this, girl that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.21,0:14:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna say that stuff\Ntoo when I beat you someday?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You act like none of it is skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're insulting all the hard\Ntraining I've been doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't say that stuff! Promise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, one of us will be\Nthe world's greatest swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.14,0:14:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll compete to see who gets there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You dummy. You're so weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.43,0:14:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me have... that sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuina's sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get stronger for her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get strong enough\Nthat my name reaches to Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be the world's\Nstrongest swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I leave Kuina's spirit and dreams... with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, I trained hard every day\Nand set out to sea to search for that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiming to become a master swordsman...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I got on a boat and went to sleep.\NI remember up to that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,After that... I can't remember\Nwhat happened after that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's weird, in the first place, is these swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When on earth did I obtain these two swords?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, they suit me quite well.\NWhat's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The most current date on the logbook\Nis the day before the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.32,0:16:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's consistent... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.81,0:16:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it... Is what\Nthat woman said all true?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.11,0:16:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a member of a pirate group...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Me...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's... There's no way that's the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But this tattoo... What on earth happened to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be in excellent spirits,\Npathetic humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,As of this moment,\Nthis island is under my control!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,On this memorable day, you will\Nall buy your lives from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who can't pay... die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.79,0:17:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we have to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.52,0:17:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I... want to live in this village...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because we're poor that I can't\Nbe Belle-Mère-san's kid anymore?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That 100,000's for my two daughters.\NI don't got enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Belle-Mère! What are you--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Gen-san. I just can't\Nsay I don't have a family...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it costs me my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, maybe we're not related by blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.10,0:17:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...but we're a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be their parent,\Neven if it's only in name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They're... my kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Belle-Mère-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I was never able to\Ndo anything mother-like for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need anything! Just don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.16,0:17:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Make your dream... come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.63,0:18:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Live...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Die with your pathetic love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nojiko! Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.37,0:18:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm joining the Arlong Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...to be a surveyor and draw sea charts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I made an agreement with Arlong\Nto buy Cocoyashi Village from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,To buy the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,For 100 million berries. If I buy\Nthe village, we can be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But, 100 million berries?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.14,0:18:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure you can earn that\Nmuch working your entire life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I will earn it! No matter what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If I ask for help from anyone,\Nmore people will get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll hurt, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Staying with the people who\Nkilled Belle-Mère-san'll hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.21,0:19:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If you survive, lots of fun things will happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine. I'll put on a big smile,\Neven when I see his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided not to cry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided to fight on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Belle-Mère-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll steal all the rest... All the rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I wake you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,--No...\N--You can go back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If I notice something unusual, I'll wake you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Sorry, Robin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I make some coffee to help us stay awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. That would be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.35,0:19:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, he's sleeping like a log,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.60,0:20:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,after saying that he was gonna\Nstay awake no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So you two weren't asleep yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was you who stole everyone's memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised that you've noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up! Everyone, wake up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I see you have some mysterious technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,--Huh?\N--Hm?
